  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed rear dormer would be an overdominant and alien feature that fails to respect the unity and rhythm along the roofline in which the host building sits. It would significantly alter the form of the roof and thus will be detrimental to the character and appearance of the existing building, nearby properties and the wider built fabric. The development is contrary to Policies D1 (Overall Design), D4 (Designing in Context), and D11 (Alterations and Extensions) of Islington Council's Unitary Development Plan (2002), and Islington's Urban Design Guide (2006)."
